description.narrative: Améliorez la qualité des drogues antimalariques en établissant la capacité du département de Food and Drug Administration de répondre à des normes internationales, et en renforçant le système de surveillance pharmaceutique.

Improve the quality of antimalarial drugs by building the capacity of the Department of Food and Drug Administration to meet international standards, and strengthening the pharmaceutical surveillance system.

Melhore a qualidade de drogas antimaláricas construindo a capacidade do departamento de Food and Drug Administration encontrar standard internacionais, e reforçando o sistema de vigilância farmacêutico.
